# Linguist language classification for GitHub
# Ensures the repository language breakdown accurately reflects the tech stack

# Core project languages — counted in GitHub's language stats
*.py linguist-language=Python
*.sql linguist-detectable
*.sql linguist-language=SQL

# Documentation — excluded from language stats
*.md linguist-documentation
docs/** linguist-documentation

# Data files — excluded from language stats
*.csv linguist-vendored

# Draw.io diagrams — excluded from language stats
*.drawio linguist-vendored
